\f0\fs22 \cf0 BlastApp is a simple, "blast everything in sight" type of game, written with Cocoa in Java. The goal of the game is to fly your helicopter through twenty levels of deadly enemy bases, mines, and ships.\
\
If you don't want to deal with actually playing the game, you can enjoy the demo mode accessible through the "Game" menu.\
\
The game is controlled through the numeric keypad. Simply use the keys around the 5 to accelerate in the indicated direction: \
