For instance, 9 accelerates you forward and upward. You can't go backwards; thus the 4 key slows you down and eventually stops your horizontal motion. Use the 5 or 0 keys on the keypad to "brake"; this will prove very useful.\
\
To shoot bullets, use the "." key in the keypad or the space bar. Your helicopter is equipped with a simple weapon system: It shoots one type of missile, in one fixed direction. You have to learn to be creative.\
\
To start a new game, hit the New button (or the n key). To pause a game and continue a paused game, use the Pause button (or the p key). Hiding the application will also pause the game.\
\
Scoring is simple: You get one point for destroying any enemy object (missiles and bullets don't count). You also get ten bonus points if you end a level in under two minutes. The points acquired during a level are multiplied by the level number. At a score of 1000 you receive a bonus helicopter. Your high score and level are remembered between games.\
\
It's possible to design custom levels for BlastApp; see LevelFileInfo.rtf in the application wrapper.\
\
Happy blasting!\
